\begin_layout Section
Plan
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This idea will be implemented as a Python package.
 Its development will follow an iterative approach: a prototype will be
 programmed and checked against annotated ECG data (readily available on
 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "PhysioNet"
target "http://physionet.org/"

\end_inset

), with successive tuning of parameters and fixing of bugs until a high
 enough detection performance or a performance plateau is reached (calculated
 with the F1-score).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Once the package is deemed mature enough it will be tested against a different
 ECG dataset (also from PhysioNet); and its F1-score once again calculated.
\end_layout

